items.title: Syrian refugees killed in Swedish gunman's attack on school
items.description: There are also reports that Bosnians were caught up in the worst shooting in Swedish history.

items.title: Panama denies US claims over free canal passages
items.description: Washington had suggested Panama had agreed to no longer charge fees for US government vessels using the waterway.

items.title: Israel minister tells army to plan for Palestinians leaving Gaza
items.description: Defence Minister Israel Katz says Gazans should have freedom of movement and critics of the war should take them in.

items.title: Strong earthquake near Santorini after days of tremors
items.description: More than 11,000 people have already left the island of Santorini in recent days.

items.title: South Korea orders airports to install bird detection cameras
items.description: The directive comes as investigators focus on bird strike as one of the causes for December's deadly plane crash.
